originalText.text: I just change Pediatrician to Dr. Jennifer Chuang, I was worried that I might noy find a Pediatrician that I feel comfortable with after being with the same Pediatrician for 22 years. But the experience that I have with Dr. Chuang was EXCELLENT, she asked a lot of questions and willing to answer any questions we may have. My daughter felt very comfortable with her and said she likes her, we like her. Definitely good choice and experience going to Dr. Chuang. Thank you Doctor.
